This is a 24 minute workout called '20 Min Interval Treadmill Workout: HIIT Run to Burn Calories & Boost Metabolism' from the channel EatMoveRest - The Stanczyks.
The workout falls under Cardio/Treadmill and Cardio/HIIT.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Advanced fitness levels.
You'll need Treadmill for this workout.
The workout has a The Firestarter and The Warrior Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate and Beginner.
The effort required is Challenging.
